event.title: Conference of FSFE President in Warsaw. September 27th at 11.10am

body.p: Karsten Geldoff, FSFE President, will attend the conference titled "Internet-based Polish database of open innovation information technology research projects – „Cooperation platform SPINACZ”". There he will give a talk on „Free and Open-Source Software and its role in building of innovative economy” at 11.10am. Assist if you are nearby! The address is Pl. Politechniki 1, 00-661, Warsaw.
